Package main.java.sorter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorHandler
    Handles errors in time registrations specified by configuration, such as impossibly fast times or multiple times.
    FinishReader
    Adds finish times to participants with the corresponding start number
    LapRaceParticipant
    The LapRaceParticipant is a subclass to Participant.
    MarathonParticipant
    MarathonParticipant is a subclass to Participant.
    Parser
    Parser parses participant files and time stamps files to find different fields (such as names, times and start number) separated by "; "
    Participant
    Abstract class Participant, can be instantiated as LapRaceParticipant or MarathonParticipant.
    ParticipantReader
    Adds participants' information (such as name) to participants with the corresponding start number
    ParticipantsList
    A collection of Participants objects.
    Reader
    Readers handles the reading of time and participant files to import to data the structure ParticipantList.
    ResultGenerator
    Generates results based on configuration file.
    StartReader
    Adds start times to participants with the corresponding start number
    TimeHandler
    A class of static methods used for calculating the difference between two different entered times and sorting lists of times.
